metadata.name: Xian hit the jade pendant directly
metadata.description:
backhand. The jade pendant was instantly broken.



Broken off, a light fragrance head on, jade in the middle of the blood is fast coagulation together, together into a drop of blood.



Blood floating in the middle of the air, very magical, very unscientific.



Just blue star data, who cares if he is scientific or not scientific.



Gazing upon this drop of blood, its attributes emerge.
